{"tid":2422440,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"郭雪芙看診「下衣失蹤」狂露腿！卻被揪P圖：不好看…她罕見回應了","createTime":"2021-02-25T07:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T12:14:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d471d5e37a9253587494b4fd564257b21e0c13","tid":2422440,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:55:17.000Z","msg":"郭雪芙儘管工作忙碌，仍不時會與粉絲分享生活點滴，只不過當她最近在Instagram上傳了2張「看診日」的照片後，引來部分網友質疑修圖：「再P反而不好看了！」對此，她也罕見正面回應了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5471/d5471372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5471%2Fd5471372.jpg&h=c05575cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲郭雪芙常和粉絲分享生活。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／aohsuehfu）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n照片中，可以看到郭雪芙戴上黑口罩，身穿杏色長版服裝，相當映襯她的白皙肌膚，即使只穿平底鞋，依然完美襯托出纖細美腿，絲毫沒有一點贅肉，不時轉頭看著待在袋子裡的愛貓Pupu，原來那天正是她帶毛小孩看診的日子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5471/d5471369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5471%2Fd5471369.jpg&h=8a447dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼郭雪芙曬美照。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／aohsuehfu）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5471/d5471370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5471%2Fd5471370.jpg&h=827072b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果，大部分網友都聚焦在郭雪芙的一雙美腿上，不只修杰楷忍不住浮出水面說「這腿真的不合理」，不少粉絲也狂讚：「太扯了啦這個腿！」但也有人認為她的腿本來就夠長了，P得更長反而不好看，對此，她則解釋自己沒P圖：「是廣角。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5471/d5471365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5471%2Fd5471365.jpg&h=ddeb6897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼郭雪芙被說腿長得不合理。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／aohsuehfu）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5471/d5471366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5471%2Fd5471366.jpg&h=53646f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，郭雪芙也曾為了維持身材付出不少心力，但她從不節食，寧可多吃蔬菜水果也不會挨餓，此外，她也養成2個吃飯的習慣，除了細嚼慢嚥，她還會邊吃邊聊天，才不會讓自己一直想吃東西。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5471/d5471368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5471%2Fd5471368.jpg&h=46ee7d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲郭雪芙曾為了維持身材付出不少心力。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／aohsuehfu）"},{"pid":"8f9ffdc82b06ada6d2d366223a7ab78ae58c96e2","tid":2422440,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:04:46.000Z","msg":"幾正...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9057d931af94d0ed8ffecbbae09225790a048743","tid":2422440,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"都唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709ad07870010ad39728456aa5c58858ef02aced","tid":2422440,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"下體失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3670d1b8d060ff958a02473c8f71cf03bf5ccbb7","tid":2422440,"uid":178241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"廣腳"},{"pid":"998ecc8c5f396b7daeb21ac4a3d756f2c8a01f72","tid":2422440,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"廣角係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595a95bbd91d8f6b77ab83da7dae3f4842cd6fa2","tid":2422440,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:42:21.000Z","msg":"廣角x2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935d5766fda66fe7519933e55052610a0e420249","tid":2422440,"uid":202276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"目測50號鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}